I think that the problem comes from a crazy empty loop in xmlvm, it doesn't sound right to wait like this:

```
        // Busy wait until the other thread finishes initializing this class
        while (!__TIB_com_nowinnovations_apps_StateMachine.classInitialized) {
            // do nothing
        }
```

For me it helped to change the code to this:
            while (!__TIB_com_nowinnovations_apps_StateMachine.classInitialized) {
                // do nothing
               [NSThread sleepForTimeInterval:0.001];
